# Stock Prediction Data Science

## Overview

This repository contains code and resources for building a stock prediction model using data science techniques. Predicting stock prices is a challenging task that involves various factors, including historical stock prices, financial indicators, news sentiment, and market trends. This project aims to provide a comprehensive guide on how to create and evaluate a stock prediction model.

